# `Future`
Can be used to pass around references to future (object or table) values.

## Syntax
```
my_ref = Future!
some_call_to_pass_the_reference_to my_ref
my_ref\now some_other_object

```

## Code
    class Future
      new: =>
        @obj=nil
        fb=getmetatable(@).__index
        setmetatable @, {
          __index: (k)=>
            o=rawget @, 'obj'
            if o
              return o[k]
            else
              return fb[k]
        }
      now: (@obj)=>
